{
  "texts": [
    "Briva-Iglesias, Vicent; João Lucas Cavalheiro Camargo & Gokhan Dogru",
    "gokhan Dogru is a visiting postdoctoral researcher at ADAPT-DCU affiliated with the Faculty of Translation and Interpreting at Universitat Autònoma de Barcelona (UAB) in the framework of Margarita Salas Grant.",
    "His research interests include terminological quality evaluation in machine translation, different use cases of MT for professional translators and the intersection of translation profession and translation technologies as well as localization."
  ]
}